## ⚠️ HIGH-PRIORITY AUDIT FINDINGS

### Compliance Audit (2026-02-07)
The codebase includes a self-audit report flagging:

1. **Privacy Act 1988** — TFN handling (currently TFN NOT collected, good)
2. **Tax Practitioners Board (TPB)** — Disclaimer required (exists but placement unclear on all screens)
3. **Tax Law Edge Cases** (7 findings):
   - Entertainment deductibility oversimplified (50% flat rule)
   - IAWO threshold history not tracked (uses $20K fallback)
   - Division 7A missing safe harbour exclusions
   - R&D offset caps not enforced ($4M annual cap)
   - Trust losses using wrong legislation (FIXED 2026-02-08)
   - FBT trustee rate should be 47% not 45%
   - Superannuation carry-forward not handled

4. **Distributed Rate Limiting Vulnerability** (MEDIUM) — in-memory only, bypassed in serverless

### Recent Fixes (2026-02-08)
- ✅ Breach detection & automated response system implemented
- ✅ Data Breach Register table created
- ✅ Trust loss recoupment fixed (Division 266/267)

